<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Welcome to the Team! Your Driver Application is Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #28a745;
            /* Green color for a positive tone */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Application Approved!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{driverName}},</p>
            <p>We are excited to inform you that your application to become a driver on our platform has been approved!
            </p>
            <p>Welcome to the team! We are looking forward to you starting to deliver orders.</p>
            <p>Please log in to your driver account to get started and view available tasks.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our driver support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>